===Tree structure of Slice Apart=== <!--T:46-->

<!--T:30-->
The Slice Apart command creates more than only the sliced object. In the following example a cube is sliced by a face.

<!--T:31-->
The slice is created and for each piece of it there is a [[Part_CompoundFilter|Part CompoundFilter]] created, thus the same slice occurs multiple times below each CompoundFilter. All these CompoundFilters are united in a Compound.

